divs: Sighting DetailsHi, my cousin took 2 pictures from his mobile phone on the 25th June 2007 at the corner of Waterworks Road & Fulcher Street Ashgrove, Queensland, next 2 the Bronco's Club. I zoomed in on these photos today as he just told me about it & they are quite interesting. The first photo, the 62, was taken about 2 minutes prior 2 the second 1, being 63, this is due 2 the phones not lighting up properly, as there were others trying 2 take pictures with their phones also. Please find attached the pictures in question.. Thanks in advance 4 your time...
